WEBVTT

00:00.767 --> 00:02.434
[silence]

00:02.502 --> 00:03.168
<i>[ Frank ] Gimme the walkie.</i>

00:03.170 --> 00:06.105
<i>[ Mac ]</i>
<i>Frank, I'm having a hard time</i>
<i>understanding what we're doing.</i>

00:06.107 --> 00:08.140
-<i> Just gimme the walkie-talkie.</i>
- All right.

00:08.142 --> 00:12.644
Why did you hide your will
in the ceiling?
I didn't do it, Charlie did it.

00:12.646 --> 00:14.313
Well, why did Charlie hide
your will in the ceiling?

00:14.315 --> 00:18.751
Because I didn't wanna crawl
around these goddamn vents.
Gimme my gun.

00:18.753 --> 00:20.386
Oh, right.
[ Gun Cocks ]
Yeah!

00:20.388 --> 00:25.157
I don't think you should be
carryin' this thing anymore.
It always gets you into trouble.

00:25.159 --> 00:26.325
Recently,
it has occurred to me...

00:26.327 --> 00:29.661
that Dennis and Deandra
stand to lose a lot of money
because they're not my kids.

00:29.663 --> 00:33.265
- They're gonna rub me out.
- I feel like you're being
very paranoid about this.

00:33.267 --> 00:36.568
If you just go to a lawyer,
you can draft up a new will,
no big deal.

00:36.570 --> 00:40.539
-Don't overthink this, trust me.
Give me the goddamn gun.
-Here.

00:40.541 --> 00:43.308
<i>Now, you think</i>
<i>you can make sense</i>
<i>of Charlie's map?</i>

00:43.310 --> 00:45.411
Because it's dark
as a well digger's ass
up here.

00:45.413 --> 00:50.215
