the subtleties of Charlie's
retardation better than me.

00:50.217 --> 00:54.286
- I can guide you right to it.
- Then you will be
handsomely rewarded.

00:54.288 --> 00:56.455
I like that.
<i>[ Door Opens ]</i>
Shit!

00:56.457 --> 00:58.257
Seal me up, seal me up!
That's them.
Get away.

00:58.259 --> 01:00.359
