You are not our big brother.
Yes, I am.

01:11.739 --> 01:15.874
So get me a beer, little bro,
before I give you
a serious noogie.

01:15.876 --> 01:17.776
Dude, I swear to God,
if you try and give me a noogie,

01:17.778 --> 01:22.414
I will yank your underwear
over your head so hard,
your asshole will rip in half.

01:22.416 --> 01:24.216
Hey-oh!
What's up, bitches?

01:24.218 --> 01:27.553
- Mac, can an asshole
rip in half?
- Like tissue paper.

01:27.555 --> 01:29.321
They behind us?

01:29.323 --> 01:30.355
No!
Lock the way out!

01:30.357 --> 01:32.357
<i>Whoa, whoa, whoa!</i>
<i>What the hell</i>
<i>are you guys doin'?</i>

01:32.359 --> 01:35.694
- [ All ] Whoa!
- Okay, okay, don't shoot, okay?
Just take whatever you want.

01:35.696 --> 01:37.329
