No matter what happens, you
and I have to stick together.

04:03.777 --> 04:07.579
You and I
will form an alliance.
We'll form an alliance.

04:08.281 --> 04:09.748
Dennis is gonna try
and have you killed.

04:09.750 --> 04:13.418
I can't say that surprises me.
No, he's gonna sell us all
down the river.

04:13.420 --> 04:17.055
