though, before Dennis does.

04:38.746 --> 04:40.712
Oh, Mac will be with us.
Mac will be with us.

04:40.714 --> 04:44.816
Frank, Frank. Come in, Frank.
McPoyles have taken us hostage.
They're threatening to kill us.

04:44.818 --> 04:47.419
