I get that will.

05:05.906 --> 05:09.041
Once that will
is safe and secure,
I'll come and help you.

05:09.043 --> 05:10.742
Will?
There's plenty of time
to do that.

05:10.744 --> 05:11.743
We can do that
some other time, dude.

05:11.745 --> 05:15.714
No.
This is all the more reason
to get that document.

05:15.716 --> 05:17.949
Who the hell knows
how it's gonna shake out
down there?

05:17.951 --> 05:22.487
<i>[ Liam ]</i>
<i>Everybody gather round!</i>
