Some loyalty, bro.

05:49.883 --> 05:52.150
Dude, what the hell, man?
You don't wanna be
on my dig team?

05:52.152 --> 05:53.518
Easy, Charlie,
I never said that.

05:53.520 --> 05:55.220
I feel like the syndrome's
making you all paranoid.

05:55.222 --> 05:57.556
It's making me crazy, dude.
Hold on, oh, my God.
He's burning up.

05:57.558 --> 05:59.791
- Sit down. You gotta sit down.
- [ Charlie ]
Oh, God. I'm getting sick.

05:59.793 --> 06:02.794
Guys, clearly Charlie's
comin' down with a nasty case
of Stockholm syndrome.

06:02.796 --> 06:04.863
Now the last thing you need
is a roomful of sick hostages.

06:04.865 --> 06:06.765
<i>So, guys,</i>
<i>do you mind if I grab</i>
<i>a couple of beers?</i>

06:06.767 --> 06:10.502
I feel we would be a lot more
relaxed if we had some beers.
Oh, and a cooler!

06:10.504 --> 06:13.839
Get a cooler, we're gonna want
to keep the beers cold.
Good idea, Charlie.

06:13.841 --> 06:15.407
- Uh-uh.
- Dude, What the hell?

06:15.409 --> 06:16.475
The cooler's
gonna keep the beer cold.

06:16.477 --> 06:19.044
How are we gonna do that
without a cooler?
I would appreciate a cold beer.

06:19.046 --> 06:22.981
We should probably all have
a cold beer inside of a cooler.
Who drinks warm beer?

06:22.983 --> 06:26.184
Let's take a vote.
All in favor of beer
and coolers-- Great.

06:26.186 --> 06:29.488
Then it's settled.
Charlie, go get a cooler.
Don't move, Charlie!

06:29.490 --> 06:32.557
No beer, no cooler.
Margaret, put your hand down.

06:32.559 --> 06:34.126
But your sister
agrees with us.
She's on our side.

06:34.128 --> 06:39.030
She's a deaf-mute.
The only reason she raised
her hand is 'cause you guys did.

06:39.032 --> 06:42.768
Really?
Let's try that
again, right?

06:42.770 --> 06:44.035
[ All Laugh ]
[ Dee ]
That's awesome.

06:44.037 --> 06:49.174
- Hey, I wonder what else
we could get her to do?
- Uh, let's blink really fast.

06:49.176 --> 06:50.375
<i>-[ Charlie Grunts</i>
<i>Rhythmically ]</i>

06:50.377 --> 06:51.476
-[ Dee ]
Oh, come on, that's awesome.

06:51.478 --> 06:55.747
All right, put your hands down
and stop blinking!
Leave Margaret alone.

06:55.749 --> 06:58.817
<i>You two, in the bathroom.</i>
<i>You two, grab some shovel.</i>

06:58.819 --> 07:00.685
Ryan, crank up the heat!

07:00.687 --> 07:03.488
We're gonna get this place
hot and clammy--

07:03.490 --> 07:06.858
[ Whispers ]
just like the McPoyles
like it.

07:07.727 --> 07:09.995
<i>[ Frank ]</i>
<i>Ah, here we go.</i>

07:09.997 --> 07:13.698
Charlie,
what are you tryin'
to tell me?

07:13.700 --> 07:16.868
"If here by now,

07:16.870 --> 07:20.105
then bad place be.

07:20.107 --> 07:24.543
Trouble time for you...

07:24.545 --> 07:28.213
