why she dressed in that.

07:48.635 --> 07:50.135
Oh, of course, that's why
they dressed like that.

07:50.137 --> 07:52.637
They're gonna stay
all nice and cool
while we get all hot and steamy.

07:52.639 --> 07:57.108
Why are you covering your mouth?
