Okay, go, good!
Good!

08:38.252 --> 08:40.151
Do you understand
what's happening?
Kinda.

08:40.153 --> 08:42.053
Do you understand what's
going on with this map?
Yes.

08:42.055 --> 08:45.323
Okay, now just walk me
through it, and we'll go
through numbers later.

08:45.325 --> 08:46.725
It's a fake map.
It's a decoy.

08:46.727 --> 08:47.626
Really?
Yep.

08:47.628 --> 08:51.863
Where's the real map?
